  <name>Contacts Application</name>
  <description>
    The Contacts Application is a reference implementation of all things Spring, Apache Geode/Pivotal GemFire, JDBC,
    JPA, along with many other technologies that are related, integrated and tested. The purpose of this application
    is to showcase the many features and capabilities of all these technologies both individually and together, as one
    cohesive, working application that demonstrates the full power, recommended practices and design patterns of these
    technologies in practice.
  </description>
